description:
This is a 31 minute workout called 'METABOLIC CONDITIONING [30 min Full Body Dumbbell Workout]' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Strength.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Advanced and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Boost your metabolism and get strong! This 30 minute full body strength session is a metabolic conditioning workout! The purpose of a metabolic conditioning workout is to increase your metabolism even after the workout is complete! We will do this with intense pushes and short rest sets! This workout is fun, but it is also tough! Lift heavy and give it your all!

30 MINUTE METABOLIC CONDITIONING WORKOUT STRUCTURE AND EXERCISES
EQUIPMENT NEEDED
- DUMBBELLS- I used a range from 15lbs to 45lbs / 7 - 20kg. Aim for a moderately heavy weight for your fitness level!

STRUCTURE
2 FULL BODY FOCUSED CIRCUITS
REPEAT EACH CIRCUIT TWICE
4 TOTAL CIRCUITS
7 EXERCISES PERCIRCUIT
WORK: 45 SECONDS REST: 10 SECONDS
REST BETWEEN ROUNDS: 45 SECONDS

I am so glad you joined me for this workout! It's always better to workout with a friend!

Kaleigh
